{"tid":1756783,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［和理sing]召喚熱愛唱歌嘅香港人","createTime":"2019-11-26T07:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T00:09:06.000Z","uid":199517,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"36a6e7414decd8b2705ead6eabf6dc4af5caeb32","tid":1756783,"uid":199517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"贏左區議會選舉之後，又係時候出嚟一齊慶祝下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家今晚7:30記得出黎尖沙咀通利琴行唱歌</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩開Busking 嘅手足幫手帶埋器材出嚟，通利琴行成日怕多人架，一多人佢就落閘，帶多啲器材就唔怕啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇玩開音樂嘅手足我哋都好需要你㗎，因為你把聲已經係最好嘅樂器，一齊出嚟咪當唱個K，平時邊有機會咁多人陪你一齊唱K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲機會梗係要好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YL1n98J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYL1n98J.jpg&h=cfa87a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivn6Sm4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fivn6Sm4.jpg&h=92105f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">附近黃店有龍門冰室同埋光榮冰室等⋯</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">附近藍店就吉野家，四洲零食物語同埋上面兩間日本餐廳⋯</span><br />\n<br />\n無法盡錄，只係俾大家參考下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁大家唱歌還唱歌，都要記得保護好自己，今日晏晝已經有狗狗係附近視察環境</span>